Package: ggtimeline
Type: Package
Title: Timeline Charts for ggplot2
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-07-14
Authors@R: c(
    person("Brooks", "Benard",
           email = "brooksbenard10@gmail.com",
           role  = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7154-744X"))
  )
Description: Create publication-ready timeline charts with 'ggplot2'.
    Draws a thick arrow axis with boxed event labels, optional era bands,
    in-arrow year labels and ticks, automatic above/below stacking, and
    full aesthetic mapping for colours, fills, and shapes.
URL: https://github.com/brooksbenard/ggtimeline
